                  <items count="16">
                    <item name="Description" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">Load a pre-defined RobotCell and matching default RobotCellState from RobotCellLibrary (e.g. 'ur5', 'ur10e', 'abb_irb4600_40_255', 'panda', 'ur5_cone_tool'). Tools and rigid bodies wired into `tools`/`rigid_bodies` are registered into the cell in one go, so no separate Add* + set_robot_cell() step is needed.</item>
